  "title": "Sales Trainer (travel opportunities)",
  "description": "<p>🚀 WE’RE HIRING SALES & MARKETING</p><p>Thinking about a career switch, or looking to grow in the sales & marketing industry?</p><p>We’re looking for people who are driven, open to learning, and ready to build something long-term. Experience is not required attitude and commitment matter more.</p><p>Who We’re Looking For</p><p>• Self-motivated individuals willing to learn</p><p>• People who enjoy working with others</p><p>• Those interested in leadership and personal growth</p><p>• Fresh graduates & career switchers are welcome</p><p>What You’ll Do 💼</p><p>• Learn practical and ethical sales & marketing skills</p><p>• Work with a team to run campaigns for established brands</p><p>• Build strong relationships with clients and customers</p><p>• Grow into leadership roles over time</p><p>🎯 What You’ll Get</p><p>• Hands-on training and guidance</p><p>• Clear, performance-based career progression</p><p>• Opportunities for local and overseas exposure</p><p>• A supportive team environment with mentorshup<br /></p><p>📩 Interested?</p><p>Send in your resume and apply now.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
